g it short and conversational.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Including stock details**\\n\\nI need to make sure I use both the code and the name when I mention stocks. In this context, I should reference 信科移动 as 688387.SH, 浙文互联 as 600986.SH, and 通光线缆 as 300265.SZ. By including these identifiers, it'll be clear for anyone looking at the information. This approach will help avoid any confusion and keep the details precise and straightforward!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 张玲，是当前这条预览的口径就只接了小市值这两条线，不是全策略总榜。\n\n我刚核了一下生成逻辑：\n- 这条“买入候选”读的是 `today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json`\n- 这个文件里买入候选是被硬分成两组：\n  - `smallcap_chip_v4_2`\n  - `smallcap_chip_v4_2b`\n- 代码里就是按这两个 strategy_id 去筛的，其他策略现在没接进这个候选展示模块\n\n所以你看到的：\n- 688387.SH 信科移动\n- 600986.SH 浙文互联\n- 300265.SZ 通光线缆\n\n都来自这两个小市值策略，属于“当前报表设计如此”，不是临时抽风。\n\n更准确地说：\n- 这条消息里的“买入候选 TOP3” = 小市值候选池预览\n- 不是 = 全部策略、全部风格、全部账户的统一排名\n\n如果你要，我可以下一步直接改成两种更合理的口径之一：\n1. 改成“全策略买入候选 TOPN”\n2. 继续保留小市值，但标题明确写成“小市值买入候选 TOPN”\n\n我个人更建议先做第 2 个，避免口径误导。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0670f03dbcdf5eed0169e421f1fe7c8199866f57b65258583e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":87269,"output":833,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776558562369,"responseId":"resp_0670f03dbcdf5eed0169e421e4ce3881998d59f0d24755e8d3"}}
